  "text": "Data were collected from free-ranging subadult and adult female polar bears without dependent young, on the sea ice of the Beaufort Sea as part of a previous study [CITATION_1] ) in April 2014 . Details of the capture methods, use of doubly labeled water, and deployment of satellite collars with tri-axial accelerometers are described elsewhere [CITATION_2] .",
